Added missing background-color/color CSS values for display templates.

Because the templates were either missing the body background-color or color
values, their appearance depended on the color scheme of the underlying
operating system. Therefore I took the liberty to add the following CSS to
templates that needed it:

body {
	background-color: white;
	color: black;
}


